      • castProtobufMessage

        public static <T extends com.google.protobuf.Message> T castProtobufMessage(com.google.protobuf.Message msg,
                                                                            Class<T> expectedType)
        Checks if the provided Message is an instance of the Class given by expectedType. Throws an IllegalArgumentException if the message is not of the expected type, otherwise, it returns the message cast as the expected type.
        Parameters:
        msg - A Protocol Buffer message.
        expectedType - The expected type of the Protocol Buffer message.
        Returns:
        The msg cast to the concrete Message type.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - If the type of the message is not the expectedType.
